c: 2
v: 159
t: "Diggah Baxxaqqa itta Astootiy Nabii Mucammad Nubuwwannuu kee tirto edde taniimiy oobisne Sinaamak Qellisa mari (yahuud kee Nasaara kinnuk) kitaabal (tawraat kee injiil kinnuk) Baxxaqqa Sinaamah hayneek lakal, Yalli woo mara isi Racmatak ken yayxeereeh gino inkih Yalli isi Racmatak ken yayxaaray ittaah ken abaarta"